[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_7kxy8")
reagent_id = "CH4"
title = "Methane"
body = "[b]Basic facts[/b]
[table=2]
[cell]Formula:[/cell][cell]CH₄[/cell]
[cell]Molar mass:[/cell][cell]16 g/mol[/cell]
[cell]State at room temperature:[/cell][cell]Gas[/cell]
[cell]Color:[/cell][cell]Colorless[/cell]
[cell]Smell:[/cell][cell]Odorless (pure methane)[/cell]
[/table]
[b]Formation reaction[/b]
C + 2H₂ → CH₄
[b]Important properties[/b]
• The simplest hydrocarbon.
• Highly flammable gas.
• Burns in oxygen to produce carbon dioxide and water.
• Main component of natural gas.
[b]Where methane is found[/b]
• In natural gas deposits.
• Produced by decomposition of organic matter in swamps and landfills.
• Formed in the digestive system of animals.
[b]Uses[/b]
• Used as a fuel for heating and cooking.
• Important energy source.
• Used in the chemical industry to produce hydrogen and other chemicals.
[b]Safety[/b]
Highly flammable and can form explosive mixtures with air."
